data.description: Sitting on .55 acres with trees on each side for added privacy, this 1,983 square foot home offers 3 bedrooms and 3 bathrooms, including a mother-in-law suite. Enjoy a large back deck and a welcoming front porch for added curb appeal. Inside, the living room features a built-in gas fireplace, while the kitchen features a beautiful tile backsplash and built-in under cabinet lighting. Stay organized with the pantry's built-in shelving and save on energy costs with adjustable flush mount lighting throughout. Call me or your agent today to schedule a tour!
